metadata.name: PHYSICALIZABLE #001
metadata.description:
PHYSICALIZABLE are 100 NFTs that can be physicalized.
This NFT project is a pursuit of the fusion of digital and physical expression.
NFT owners will have the right to purchase the limited physical drawing and to create their own work using the SVG that we give.

PHYSICALIZABLE is created by a process that combines the digital and the physical.
A total of 100 graphics designed to represent "characters in a geometric world" are created by an automatic generation process. The digital data is then converted into physical drawings using a unique method called "Plotter Drawing" to complete the physical work.

Please see [PHYSICALIZABLE WEB](https://physicalizable.com) for details.

Physicalization is a limit of 10 per NFT. 
Please check the [current status](https://bit.ly/3p3gJF3).

[Download the SVG](https://bit.ly/3LMaNtL) here.
